data.description: Situated on an interior lot with no HOA, this 1804 square foot home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a custom built kitchen, and plenty of cabinetry to provide ample storage. The kitchen opens to both the dining and living spaces, with access to the backyard off of the kitchen area. Additional amenities include ann updated primary bathroom, wood burning fire place, no carpet throughout, and exterior storage shed. The attic access from the garage is truly one-of-a-kind with lighting, carpet, and approximately 275 SF of climate controlled attic storage. Schedule your private tour today, welcome home!
